{"tid":1827853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員新屯門中心外貼連儂牆斷正 遭帶署調查","createTime":"2020-01-17T09:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T09:47:50.000Z","uid":264806,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e86a3a100af4628d19be09b7c69c0e9735b00ed3","tid":1827853,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200117/bkn-20200117095836736-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200117%2Fbkn-20200117095836736-0117_00822_001.html&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcypKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=f34b46ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200117/bkn-20200117095836736-0117_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n修例風波：警員新屯門中心外貼連儂牆斷正 遭帶署調查<br />\n<br />\n修例風波延續超過半年，示威者在多區張貼文宣組成「連儂牆」，有關「連儂牆」的衝突亦屢有發生。今日凌晨(17日)3時許，一批市民在屯門龍門路新屯門中心一帶，港鐵屯門車廠對開空間疑擬建立「連儂牆」。期間有巡警經過時揭發事件，多名警員隨即上前制止眾人，並在場截查5男3女(13-60歲)。<br />\n經調查，警方在現場人士身上檢獲一批文宣、現金及電鑽，遂以涉嫌「藏有工具可作非法用途」將眾人帶署調查。據悉該批人士中包括一名現役警員，消息指他當時與其女友及女友父母在場作案。"},{"pid":"03999191b34eea0d77120d3e20f8225becf1ac99","tid":1827853,"uid":148958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"藍絲定手足?"},{"pid":"c231ed5c087d9c53674b9aff01e4f1704d939e97","tid":1827853,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:40:45.000Z","msg":"貼連儂牆可以點&quot;斷正&quot;呢?<br />\n垃圾東網"},{"pid":"de14f6020fb862caae7e5971f04960ab85f003d4","tid":1827853,"uid":313514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a67cc699bc3bb90e862cce72ca52e6f1a749ad3","tid":1827853,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03999191b34eea0d77120d3e20f8225becf1ac99","tid":1827853,"uid":148958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"藍絲定手足?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"白警被捉,圍內想捉白警,叫白警滲透唔好辭職